reviewText: The Best movie on this subject until Nancy Spielberg made Above and Beyond.
It was what I expected. Good documentary.
IT IS A VERY GREAT STORY FOR ALL LOVERS OF ISRAEL!

This DVD covers the murky start of the Israeli Air Force. While it is a good with a almost homemade quality to it and is a nice addition to my film collection. The Subject really calls for a professional studio to take up the story.
